## 2.4

由上题可知

$$\frac{{{\partial ^4}W\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^4}}} = \frac{{m{\omega ^2}}}{{EI}}W\left( x \right)$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
\int_0^L {\frac{{m\omega _i^2}}{{EI}}{W_j}\left( x \right){W_i}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} &= \int_0^L {\frac{{{\partial ^4}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^4}}}{W_j}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} \\
&= \left. {\frac{{{\partial ^3}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^3}}}{W_j}\left( x \right)} \right|_0^L - \int_0^L {\frac{{{\partial ^3}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^3}}}\frac{{\partial {W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}{\rm{d}}x} \\
&= -\left. {\frac{M}{EI} \omega_i ^2 W_i(x){W_j}\left( x \right)} \right|_{x = 0} - \int_0^L {\frac{{{\partial ^3}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^3}}}\frac{{\partial {W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}{\rm{d}}x} \\
&= -\left. {\frac{M}{EI}\omega_i ^2 W_i(x){W_j}\left( x \right)} \right|_{x = 0} - \left. {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}\frac{{\partial {W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}} \right|_0^L + \int_0^L {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\rm{d}}x} \\
&= -\left. {\frac{M}{EI}\omega_i ^2 W_i(x){W_j}\left( x \right)} \right|_{x = 0} + k \left. {\frac{{{\partial}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}}\frac{{\partial {W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}} \right|_{x = L} + \int_0^L {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\rm{d}}x}
\end{align*}
$$

所以


$$
\omega _i^2 \left(\int_0^L {\frac{{m}}{{EI}}{W_j}\left( x \right){W_i}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} + \left. {\frac{M}{EI}\omega_i ^2 W_i(x){W_j}\left( x \right)} \right|_{x = 0}\right) = k \left. {\frac{{{\partial}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}}\frac{{\partial {W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}} \right|_{x = L} + \int_0^L {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\rm{d}}x}
$$

由对称性

$$
\omega _j^2 \left(\int_0^L {\frac{{m}}{{EI}}{W_j}\left( x \right){W_i}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} + \left. {\frac{M}{EI}\omega_i ^2 W_i(x){W_j}\left( x \right)} \right|_{x = 0}\right) = k \left. {\frac{{{\partial}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x}}}\frac{{\partial {W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial x}}} \right|_{x = L} + \int_0^L {\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}\frac{{{\partial ^2}{W_j}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^2}}}{\rm{d}}x}
$$

所以

$$
(\omega _i^2 - \omega_j^2) \left(\int_0^L {\frac{{m}}{{EI}}{W_j}\left( x \right){W_i}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} + \left. {\frac{M}{EI} W_i(x){W_j}\left( x \right)} \right|_{x = 0}\right) = 0
$$

由$\omega_i \neq \omega_j$, 则有

$$
\left(\int_0^L {m{W_j}\left( x \right){W_i}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} + \left. {M W_i(x){W_j}\left( x \right)} \right|_{x = 0}\right) = 0
$$

故满足正交性

## 2.5



$$
c_i^2 \left(\int_0^L {m{W_i}\left( x \right){W_i}\left( x \right){\rm{d}}x} + \left. {M W_i(x){W_i}\left( x \right)} \right|_{x = 0}\right) = 1
$$

计算得

$$
\begin{cases}
c_1 &= 0.329234 \frac{1}{\sqrt{mL}}\\
c_2 &= 0.094979 \frac{1}{\sqrt{mL}}\\
c_3 &= 0.052771 \frac{1}{\sqrt{mL}}\\
\end{cases}
$$

取

$$w\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{W_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}$$

代入

$$m\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{W_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} + EI\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^4}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^4}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} = 0$$

同时积分则有

$$
m\int_0^L {{W_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{W_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} {\rm{d}}x + EI} \int_0^L {{W_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^4}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^4}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} {\rm{d}}x} = 0
$$

方程解耦为

$$
{\ddot \eta _i} + \omega _i^2{\eta _i} = 0,{\rm{ }}i = 1,2,3
$$

解为

$$
\begin{array}{l}
{\eta _1}\left( t \right) = {C_1}\sin {\omega _1}t + {C_2}\cos {\omega _1}t\\
{\eta _2}\left( t \right) = {C_3}\sin {\omega _2}t + {C_4}\cos {\omega _2}t\\
{\eta _3}\left( t \right) = {C_5}\sin {\omega _3}t + {C_6}\cos {\omega _3}t
\end{array}
$$

易知

$$
\int_0^L {m{W_i}\left( x \right)w\left( {x,0} \right){\rm{d}}x} = \sum\limits_{j = 1}^3 {\int_0^L {m{W_i}{W_j}{\eta _j}\left( 0 \right){\rm{d}}x} }
$$

依据题意$w(x, 0) = y(x, 0), \dot w(x, 0) = \dot y(x, 0)$有

$$
{\eta _i}\left( 0 \right) = \int_0^L {m{W_i}\left( x \right)w\left( {x,0} \right){\rm{d}}x}
$$

所以

$$
\begin{array}{l}
{\eta _1}\left( 0 \right) = 0.33755m{y_0}L\\
{\eta _2}\left( 0 \right) = - 1.18436 m{y_0}L\\
{\eta _3}\left( 0 \right) = 0.157293 m{y_0}L
\end{array}
$$

$${\dot \eta _i}\left( 0 \right) = \int_0^L {m{W_i}\left( x \right)\dot w\left( {x,0} \right){\rm{d}}x} = 0$$

代入

$$
w\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{W_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}
$$

其中

$$
\begin{cases}
\eta_1 = 0.33755m{y_0}L \cos \omega_1 t \\
\eta_2 = - 1.18436m{y_0}L \cos \omega_2 t \\
\eta_3 = 0.157293m{y_0}L \cos \omega_3 t\\
\end{cases}
$$

## 2.6

$$m\int_0^L {{W_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{W_i}\left( x \right)\frac{{{\partial ^2}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)}}{{\partial {t^2}}}} {\rm{d}}x + EI} \int_0^L {{W_j}\left( x \right)\sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {\frac{{{\partial ^4}{W_i}\left( x \right)}}{{\partial {x^4}}}{\eta _i}\left( t \right)} {\rm{d}}x} = \int_0^L {{W_j}\left( x \right)f\left( {x,t} \right){\rm{d}}x}$$

方程解耦

$$
\begin{array}{l}
{{\ddot \eta }_i} + \omega _i^2{\eta _i} = {F_0}\int_0^L {{W_i}\left( x \right)\delta \left( {x - \frac{{3L}}{4}} \right)\left[ {r\left( t \right) - r\left( {t - T} \right)} \right]{\rm{d}}x} \\
\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\;\; = {F_0}{W_i}\left( {\frac{{3L}}{4}} \right)\left[ {r\left( t \right) - r\left( {t - T} \right)} \right],\;\;i = 1,2,3
\end{array}
$$

即

$$
\begin{array}{l}
{{\ddot \eta }_1} + \omega _1^2{\eta _1}\; = {F_0}{W_1}\left( {\frac{{3L}}{4}} \right)\left[ {r\left( t \right) - r\left( {t - T} \right)} \right]\\
{{\ddot \eta }_2} + \omega _2^2{\eta _2}\; = {F_0}{W_2}\left( {\frac{{3L}}{4}} \right)\left[ {r\left( t \right) - r\left( {t - T} \right)} \right]\\
{{\ddot \eta }_3} + \omega _3^2{\eta _3}\; = {F_0}{W_3}\left( {\frac{{3L}}{4}} \right)\left[ {r\left( t \right) - r\left( {t - T} \right)} \right]
\end{array}
$$

解得

$$
\begin{array}{l}
{\eta _1}\; =\frac{{1.29176{F_0}{L^4}}}{{EI\sqrt {mL} }}\left[ {\left( {t - \sin \left( {{\omega _1}t} \right)} \right)u\left( t \right) - \left( {\left( {t - T} \right) - \sin \left( {{\omega _1}\left( {t - T} \right)} \right)} \right)u\left( {t - T} \right)} \right]\\
{\eta _2}\; = \frac{{-0.0817391{F_0}{L^4}}}{{EI\sqrt {mL} }}\left[ {\left( {t - \sin \left( {{\omega _2}t} \right)} \right)u\left( t \right) - \left( {\left( {t - T} \right) - \sin \left( {{\omega _2}\left( {t - T} \right)} \right)} \right)u\left( {t - T} \right)} \right]\\
{\eta _3}\; = \frac{{0.0161349{F_0}{L^4}}}{{EI\sqrt {mL} }}\left[ {\left( {t - \sin \left( {{\omega _3}t} \right)} \right)u\left( t \right) - \left( {\left( {t - T} \right) - \sin \left( {{\omega _3}\left( {t - T} \right)} \right)} \right)u\left( {t - T} \right)} \right]
\end{array}
$$

代入

$$
w\left( {x,t} \right) = \sum\limits_{i = 1}^3 {{W_i}\left( x \right){\eta _i}\left( t \right)}
$$

即可
